window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Best-selling author narrator team of <i>Solitude: Dimension Space, Book One</i></p> <p>Humans rule the galaxy…today!</p> <p>The Milkyway’s predominant species discovers a lost colony of their ancestors—humans—populating today’s Earth. Then our genetic link draws the attention and enmity of their galactic rivals.</p> <p>When a plan to elevate present-day Earth leads to an alien invasion, a small, multinational military task force is all that stands between humanity and certain annihilation. If you like action-packed novels, then you’ll love the electrifying action in this apocalyptic military thriller.</p> <p>Grab book one today!</p> <p><i>Independence Day </i>meets<i> The X-Files</i> when Air Force fighter pilots Jake Giard and Sandra Fitzpatrick join a decades-old secret project to integrate today's Earth into a galactic government. But when a galactic civil war spills onto our shores, plunging the planet into an otherworldly post-apocalyptic hell, can Jake and Sandy save humanity from extinction?</p>"; 
